public interface Package
extends Data

This interface represents a package in the framework object model. A package contains other packages, classes, or datatypes.

public java.util.Collection getXMIContents()
Return the packages and XMI classes directly contained in this package. If there are none, this method returns an empty collection; otherwise, this method returns an unmodifiable collection of classes and packages.
